assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Veste S.A. Estilo designs and retails clothing and clothing accessories primarily for women and men in Brazil. It also offers decoration, hygiene, and cosmetic products. The company sells its products through its stores, online sales, and multi-brand stores. As of December 31, 2021, it owned and operated 208 stores under the Le Lis Blanc Deux, Dudalina, Bo.Bô, John John, Noir Lelis, Individual, and Rosa Chá; and operated 17 outlets, and 27 franchises, as well as 2 distribution centers in the states of São Paulo and Goiás. The company was formerly known as Restoque Comércio e Confecções de Roupas S.A. Veste S.A. Estilo was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in São Paulo, Brazil.
